title: TikTok Fined by Irish Regulator Over Misuse of Children's Data
description: Irish authorities fined TikTok $367 million, saying that it breached the country’s data-protection laws, including what it said was the misuse of children’s information.

title: Apple Counts on Wireless Carriers to Avoid an iPhone Slump
description: AT&T, Verizon and T-Mobile are returning to deep discounts on phones for customers who commit to top-tier plans.

title: Can You Have a Career Without a Smartphone?
description: One therapist is on a mission to get professionals to re-evaluate their relationship to their devices. These five tips might help.
